headline: Jacobs Leading Resilient Infrastructure Design in Puerto Rico
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been selected by the Puerto Rico Aqueduct and Sewer Authority (PRASA) to design the Mayagüez Ocean Outfall Replacement, part of PRASA's Capital Improvement Program to modernize and strengthen Puerto Rico's water infrastructure.
